{"tid":1483583,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"攻其無備，出其不意。","createTime":"2019-08-18T12:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T02:25:37.000Z","uid":17641,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"db2ef2d3df84ccbd64648d88cc852d401dac0317","tid":1483583,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:21:44.000Z","msg":"趁敵人沒有防備的時候進攻，採取敵人意想不到的出擊行動。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb31b279f0461dda165f48d22701e33d759b29d","tid":1483583,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:22:20.000Z","msg":"善用兵者，避其銳氣，擊其惰歸。<br />\n孫子把士氣分為三種：朝氣銳，晝氣惰，暮氣歸。善於指揮作戰的將領，要避開敵人的銳氣，等到敵人士氣衰落、疲憊時再去攻擊它。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7fea07e1e120e215e4336552ee9cb2153fa2a78","tid":1483583,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84857ec946f817f6b018961a93eeacba65197f23","tid":1483583,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f7b5a88d3461ca86719c5d01d51b5ee44adc7a1","tid":1483583,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:57:31.000Z","msg":"即係冷氣軍師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfafe1071e66ecb78c233569eab9131ead1d604","tid":1483583,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:24:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22277998b6a0c66467660eb30f6020aae08b76c0","tid":1483583,"uid":277263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:25:37.000Z","msg":"陳帆呼籲市民：寧願參加其他活動都好過堵塞機場<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1498684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">